Description: console for intrusion databases
 BASE is the Basic Analysis and Security Engine. It is based on
 the code from the Analysis Console for Intrusion Databases
 (ACID) project. This application provides a web front-end to
 query and analyze the alerts coming from a SNORT IDS system.
 
